0%94%20including%20data%20like%20names%2C%20phone%20numbers%2C%20passport%20numbers%2C%20visa%20information%2C%20and%20partial%20Social%20Security%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcvs-database-of-1-billion-data-points-inadvertently-leaked-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeremiah%20Fowler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20security%20researcher%20who%20co-founded%20the%20consulting%20firm%20Security%20Discovery%2C%20said%20he%20didn't%20know%20how%20long%20the%20data%20had%20been%20exposed%20but%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20database%20was%20soon%20locked%20once%20he%20contacted%20the%20recruiter%20in%20September.%20He%20said%20New%20Jersey-based%20Alltech%20Consulting%20Services%20never%20responded%20to%20his%20notices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlltech%20representatives%20also%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20specifically%20about%20the%20security%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFowler%20on%20Monday%20published%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.websiteplanet.com%2Fnews%2Falltechconsultinginc-breach-report%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20indicating%20that%20Alltech%20left%20its%20database%20of%20job%20candidate%20information%20unsecured%20without%20a%20password.%20That%20left%20the%20personal%20identifying%20information%20of%20about%20216%2C000%20tech%20job%20candidates%20exposed.%20Because%20the%20door%20was%20essentially%20left%20unlocked%2C%20someone%20trying%20to%20steal%20identities%20wouldn't%20have%20needed%20to%20hack%20into%20Alltech's%20database%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20search%20that%20hard%20%E2%80%94%20to%20find%20the%20information%2C%20Fowler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlltech%20says%20on%20its%20website%20that%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%201%2C000%20companies%26quot%3B%20rely%20on%20its%20services%20to%20connect%20them%20with%20tech%20professionals.%20Business%20Insider%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20verify%20this%20independently.