0jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fmilestone-moments%5C%22%3EMilestone%20Moments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20about%20financial%20planning%20for%20major%20life%20events.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20February%202020%2C%20I%20started%20my%20first%20full-time%20office%20job.%20When%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20about%20a%20month%20later%2C%20I%20started%20working%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20years%20I%20continued%20to%20work%20from%20home%2C%20and%20I%20found%20that%20it%20worked%20much%20better%20for%20me%20than%20working%20in%20person%20did.%20When%20my%20company%20required%20us%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20the%20added%20stress%20and%20commuting%20time%20convinced%20me%20I%20needed%20to%20look%20elsewhere%20for%20a%20remote%20job.%20But%20I%20found%20myself%20too%20tired%20to%20effectively%20job%20search%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20workday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20weighed%20my%20options%2C%20checked%20my%20emergency%20fund%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20quit%20my%20job%20before%20finding%20another%20position.%20I%20don't%20regret%20doing%20it%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20I'd%20used%20more%20effective%20methods%20to%20build%20up%20my%20emergency%20fund%20beforehand%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20creating%20a%20budget%20and%20using%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Ehigh-yield%20savings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20so%20I'd%20have%20more%20time%20to%20find%20a%20job%20that%20was%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20my%20career%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20I%20could%20have%20done%20better%20when%20saving%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20quit%2C%20I%20had%20enough%20money%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%