-strategy-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20zoomed%20higher%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20win%20last%20week%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20notching%20a%20quick%205%25%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20while%20Trump's%20win%20opens%20the%20stock%20market%20to%20potentially%20more%20upside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarket-impact-presidential-election-scenarios-trump-harris-stocks-bonds-crypto-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evia%20tax%20cuts%20and%20deregulation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-risk-outlook-trump-deportation-tariff-anthony-scaramucci-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emakes%20it%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20other%20risks.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20chief%20market%20economist%20John%20Higgins%20of%20Capital%20Economics%2C%20the%20biggest%20risk%20looming%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20China%2C%20specifically%2C%20its%20potential%20reaction%20to%20another%20Trump%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20the%20biggest%20risk%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20given%20that%20a%20bubble%20in%20the%20index%20has%20been%20inflated%20by%20hype%20around%20AI%2C%20would%20be%20a%20retaliatory%20clampdown%20by%20China%20on%20US%20big-tech%20firms'%20operations%20in%20its%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20Higgins%20wrote%20in%20a%20Monday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20campaign%20trail%2C%20Trump%20proposed%20a%2060%25%20tariff%20on%20all%20goods%20imported%20from%20China%2C%20which%20would%20be%20a%20sharp%20escalation%20from%20the%2025%25%20tariffs%20he%20placed%20on%20a%20select%20list%20of%20goods%20during%20his%20first%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Trump's%20proposed%2060%25%20tariff%20against%20China%