%20Pacific%20for%20sea%20trials.%20The%20unmanned%20surface%20vessels%20-%20Sea%20Hunter%2C%20Sea%20Hawk%2C%20Mariner%20and%20Ranger%20-%20departed%20Southern%20California%20in%20August%202023%20and%20returned%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20AMCA%20Program%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20developing%20its%205.5%20generation%20Advanced%20Medium%20Combat%20Aircraft%20which%20will%20have%20stealth%20capabilities%20and%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organization%20chief%20said%20the%20induction%20is%20expected%20by%202035.%C2%A0Air%20Force's%20latest%20induction%2C%20the%20Rafale%20fighter%20jet%2C%20is%20a%204.5%20generation%20multi-role%20aircraft%20that%20is%20deployed%20in%20the%20north%20in%20Ambala%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Hashimara%20in%20Assam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20China%20has%20deployed%20the%20J-20%20fighter%20jets%20close%20to%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%2C%20experts%20have%20inferred%20that%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20conflict%2C%20standalone%20weapon%20systems%20like%20surface-to-air%20missiles%2C%20air-to-air%20missiles%20and%20air%20defence%20systems%20will%20play%20a%20huge%20role%20for%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20to%20combat%20and%20outmanoeuvre%20the%20Chinese.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatch%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Findia-to-induct-5-5-gen-stealth-fighter-jet-amca-by-2035-drdo-chairman-825552%5C%22%3E'India%20To%20Induct%205.5-Gen%20Stealth%20Fighter%20Jet%20AMCA%20By%202035%3A%20DRDO%20Chairman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20DRDO%20showcased%2040%20indigenously%20developed%20advanced%20systems%20and%20technologies%20at%20the%20International%20Defence%20Aviation%20Exposition%20IDAX%202024%20during%20the%20Tarang%20Shakti%20exercise%20at%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Sulur.%20On%20India's%20first%205.5-generation%20stealth%20aircraft%2C%20Advanced%20Medium%20Combat%20Aircraft%20(AMCA)%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Defenc