5%20Held%20In%20Telangana%20In%20Land%20Row%20Violence%20In%20Revanth%20Reddy's%20Constituency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2055%20people%20in%20Telangana's%20Vikarabad%20district%20were%20detained%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20allegedly%20attacking%20government%20officials%20during%20a%20protest%20against%20acquisition%20of%20land%20for%20a%20pharmaceutical%20project.%20The%20protest%20took%20place%20in%20Lagacharla%20village%20of%20Dudyala%20mandal%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20Kodangal%20assembly%20seat%20represented%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20A%20Revanth%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20officials%20-%20Kodangal%20Area%20Development%20Authority%20(KADA)%20chairman%20Venkat%20Reddy%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Srinivas%20Reddy%2C%20Additional%20Collector%20Lingya%20Naik%20and%20Mandal%20Revenue%20Officer%20Vijay%20Kumar%20-%20sustained%20injuries%20after%20villagers%20attacked%20the%20officials%20with%20sticks%20and%20threw%20stones%20at%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20General%20of%20Police%20(Multi%20Zone%20II)%20V.%20Satyanarayana%20told%20news%20agency%20IANS%20that%20the%20attack%20on%20officials%20was%20%26quot%3Bpre-planned%26quot%3B%20allegedly%20by%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20youth%20wing%20leader%20B%20Suresh%20Raj%2C%20who%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatyanarayana%20also%20said%20that%20police%20believe%20100-110%20people%20participated%20in%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20take%20stringent%20action%20against%20those%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20attack%20and%20those%20who%20instigated%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20when%20a%20team%20of%20officials%2C%20led%20by%20Collector%20Prateek%20Jain%2C%20visited%20the%20village%20to%20seek%20the%20locals'%20opinion%20on%20the%20proposed%20land%20acquisition%20for%20the%20pharma%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20aware%20of%20the%20details%20said%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20acquire%201%2C358%20acres%20of%20land%20for%20the%20pharma%20project.%20Farmers%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20the%20compensation%20offered%20is%20lower%20than%20market%20rates%2C%20and%20have%20expressed%20their%20apprehensions%20about%20losing%20their%20land%20and%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20Collector's%20office%20had%20set%20up%20a%20camp%20on%20Monday%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Lagacharla%20to%20seek%20public%20opinion%20when%20Raj%20approached%20the%20officials%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20visit%20the%20village%20instead%20for%20the%20discussion.%20As%20the%20collector%20and%20his%20team%20reached%20the%20spot%2C%20the%20villagers%20attacked%20them%20and%20raised%20slogans%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bcollector%20go%20back%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRaj%20had%20people%20ready%20to%20attack%20the%20officers%20who%20showed%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Satyanarayana%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20staffers%20at%20the%20Collector's%20office%20staged%20a%20dharna%20against%20the%20attack%2C%20even%20as%20the%20official%20said%20he%20was%20not%20attacked%20by%20the%20villagers.%20Other%20government%20employees%20in%20the%20district%20boycotted%20their%20duties%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20employees%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20state%20wore%20black%20badges%2C%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Telangana%20minister%20Sridhar%20Babu%20said%20the%20state%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20serious%20view%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20which%20was%20planned%20by%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20elements%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20stop%20development%20in%20Telangana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20dismissed%20BRS%20working%20president%20K%20T%20Rama%20Rao's%20allegation%20that%20the%20pharma%20project%20would%20benefit%20a%20relative%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731425160000%2C%22visual%2