0compared%20to%20the%20past%20but%20remains%20unfazed%20by%20the%20possibility%20of%20someone%20surpassing%20him.%20The%20five-time%20world%20champion%2C%20who%20held%20the%20title%20from%202013%20to%202023%2C%20chose%20not%20to%20defend%20his%20crown%2C%20citing%20lack%20of%20motivation.%20Despite%20stepping%20back%20from%20classical%20tournaments%2C%20Carlsen's%20reign%20at%20the%20top%20is%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20and%20most%20dominant%20in%20chess%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20play%20a%20lot%20of%20classical%20chess%2C%20so%20whenever%20somebody%20is%20going%20to%20pass%20me%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20particularly%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2033-year-old%20Norwegian%20said%20during%20a%20media%20interaction%20ahead%20of%20the%20Tata%20Steel%20Chess%20India%20Rapid%20and%20Blitz%20tournament%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20surpass%20me%2C%20but%20we'll%20see%20when%20it%20happens.%20I%20think%20it%20sort%20of%20depends%20on%20others.%26quot%3B%20Carlsen%20also%20suggested%20that%20chess%20ratings%20may%20not%20carry%20the%20same%20weight%20they%20did%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20been%20deflation%20in%20chess%20ratings%2C%20so%20a%20level%20of%20ELO%202830%20would%20probably%20correspond%20to%202850%20about%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20reached%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20noted%20Carlsen%2C%20who%20currently%20has%20a%20FIDE%20rating%20of%202831.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20held%20the%20world%20number%201%20spot%20almost%20continuously%20since%20July%201%2C%202011%2C%20Carlsen%20first%20achieved%20the%20top%20ranking%20in%20January%202010%20at%20the%20age%20of%2019%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20player%20to%20reach%20that%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20briefly%20losing%20it%20in%20mid%202011%2C%20he%20reclaimed%20the%20top%20spot%20and%20has%20dominated%20it%20ever%20since.%20Throughout%20his%20career%2C%20Carlsen%20has%20set%20multiple%20records%2C%20including%20the%20highest%20FIDE%20rating%20ever%20recorded%20at%202882%20in%20May%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20opting%20out%20of%20the%20World%20Championship%20in%202023%2C%20Carlsen%20has%20%26quot%3Bpicked%20and%20chosen%26quot%3B%20tournaments%20with%20formats%20and%20opponents%20he%20finds%20exciting%2C%20focusing%20on%20rapid%2C%20blitz%2C%20and%20other%20flexible%20events%20that%20align%20with%20his%20evolving%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20younger%20generation%20of%20players%2C%20Carlsen%20conveyed%20his%20respect%20for%20their%20progress%20while%20noting%20that%20they%20don't%20always%20measure%20up%20to%20his%20level%2C%20a%20statement%20more%20reflective%20of%20his%20confidence%20than%20arrogance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20testing%20myself%20against%20the%20younger%20generation.%20I'm%20always%20curious%20to%20see%20how%20much%20they've%20improved%20since%20the%20last%20time.%20It%20turns%20out%20they%20have%20improved%2C%20but%20not%20always%20enough.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20look%20forward%20to%20seeing%20all%20the%20Indian%20chess%20fans.%20It's%20quite%20chaotic%3B%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20I%20don't%20do%20play%20here%20every%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Carlsen%20who%20is%20here%20to%20play%20the%20tournament%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarlsen%20has%20won%20the%20World%20Rapid%20Chess%20Championship%20four%20times%20(2014%2C%202015%2C%202019%2C%20and%202022)%20and%20the%20World%20Blitz%20Chess%20Championship%20five%20times%20(2009%2C%202014%2C%202017%2C%202018%2C%20and%202019)%2C%20making%20him%20one%20of%20the%20most%20versatile%20and%20dominant%20world%20champions%20across%20different%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20younger%20generation%20of%20chess%20players%2C%20Carlsen%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20interesting%20to%20see%20a%20different%20brand%20of%20chess.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20older%20players%20of%20my%20generation%20are%20not%20going%20to%20surprise%20you%20in%20a%20major%20way%20in%20terms%20of%20where%20they%20stand%2C%20but%20with%20the%20younger%20generation%2C%20it's%20interesting%20to%20try%20and%20understand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarlsen%20began%20his%20reign%20after%20defeating%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20in%20the%20World%20Championship%20in%20Chennai%20in%202013%20and%20he%20feels%20the%20country%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20to%20Chennai%20in%20August%20(2013)%2C%20to%20look%20at%20the%20facilities%20and%20so%20on.%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I'm%20going%20to%20meet%20some%20of%20the%20better%20kids%20in%20the%20area%20to%20play%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20like%20half%20of%20the%20kids%20are%20now%20either%20GMs%20or%20some%20of%20them%20are%20even%20playing%20in%20top%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20has%20changed.%20Those%20kids%20back%20then%20are%20now%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Olympiad-winning%20team.%20Indian%20chess%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20since%20then%2C%20much%20thanks%20to%20Anand%20and%20what%20he%20did%20for%20Indian%20chess%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarlsen%20was%20also%20impressed%20with%20three-year-old%20chess%20prodigy%20from%20the%20city%20Anish%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20recently%20became%20the%20youngest%20FIDE-rated%20chess%20player%20in%20the%20world%20with%20a%20rating%20of%201555.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20it's%20amazing%20to%20see%20the%20level%20he's%20at.%20My%20nephew%20is%20turning%204%2C%20he's%20a%20bright%20young%20child%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20him%20getting%20a%20rating%20of%201500%20anytime%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20impressive.%20Most%20of%20all%2C%20try%20to%20enjoy%20as%20much%20as%20you%20can.%20Don't%20think%20about%20ratings%2C%20results%2C%20titles%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20They%20will%20come%20automatically%3B%20just%20do%20what%20you%20love%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20signed%20off%2C%20while%20posing%20for%20a%20photo%20with%20the%20kid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731424740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fqm74ahr8_r-praggnanandhaa-vs-magnus-carlsen_650x400_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fcarlsen-unfazed-by-prospect-of-being-surpassed-says-chess-ratings-are-deflated-these-days-7003567%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Carlsen%20also%20said%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20'deflation'%20in%20the%20significance%20of%20chess%20ratings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saudi%20crown%20prince%20condemns%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98genocide'%20against%20Palestinians%2C%20warns%20against%20military%20action%20in%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731424657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115224245%2Cimgsize-1721145.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsaudi-crown-prince-condemns-israels-genocide-against-palestinians-warns-against-military-action-in-iran%2Farticleshow%2F115221471.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115221471.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsaudi-crown-prince-condemns-israels-genocide-against-palestinians-warns-against-military-action-in-iran%2Farticleshow%2F115221471.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsaudi-crown-prince-condemns-israels-genocide-against-palestinians-warns-against-military-action-in-iran%2Famp_articleshow%2F115221471.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsaudi-crown-prince-condemns-israels-genocide-against-palestinians-warns-against-military-action-in-iran%2Famp_articleshow%2F115221471.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Potential%20For%20Life%20Found%20On%20Uranus'%20Moons%2C%20Scientists%20Reveal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20planet%20Uranus%20and%20its%20five%20largest%20moons%20may%20not%20be%20the%20cold%2C%20lifeless%20worlds%20scientists%20once%20believed.%20Instead%2C%20they%20could%20have%20hidden%20oceans%20and%20even%20the%20potential%20to%20support%20life%2C%20according%20to%20new%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20our%20knowledge%20of%20Uranus%20comes%20from%20NASA's%20Voyager%202%20mission%2C%20which%20visited%20nearly%2040%20years%20ago.%20However%2C%20a%20recent%20analysis%20reveals%20that%20Voyager's%20encounter%20occurred%20during%20an%20intense%20solar%20storm%2C%20potentially%20skewing%20our%20perception%20of%20the%20Uranian%20system%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgk1333k0ypo%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUranus%2C%20an%20icy%2C%20ringed%20planet%20at%20the%20solar%20system's%20edge%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20coldest%20and%20most%20unusual%20planets%20due%20to%20its%20extreme%20tilt%2C%20making%20it%20appear%20as%20if%20it%20had%20been%20tipped%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20findings%20reveal%20that%20Voyager%202's%20visit%20coincided%20with%20severe%20solar%20activity%2C%20which%20may%20have%20temporarily%20disrupted%20the%20planet's%20magnetic%20field%20and%20swept%20away%20atmospheric%20material.%20For%20decades%2C%20this%20led%20scientists%20to%20a%20possibly%20inaccurate%20view%20of%20Uranus%20and%20its%20moons%2C%20explained%20Dr%20William%20Dunn%20from%20University%20College%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20results%20suggest%20the%20Uranian%20system%20might%20be%20far%20more%20intriguing%20than%20we%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Dunn%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20may%20be%20moons%20there%20with%20conditions%20that%20could%20support%20life%2C%20possibly%20hiding%20oceans%20below%20their%20surfaces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELinda%20Spilker%2C%20a%20young%20scientist%20on%20the%20Voyager%20team%20when%20the%20Uranus%20data%20arrived%2C%20now%20serves%20as%20the%20project%20scientist%20for%20the%20Voyager%20missions.%20She%20expressed%20excitement%20about%20the%20new%20findings%2C%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41550-024-02389-3%5C%22%3ENature%20Astronomy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20thrilling%20to%20think%20there's%20potential%20for%20life%20in%20the%20Uranian%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BBC%20News.%20She%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20amazing%20that%20scientists%20are%20still%20uncovering%20new%20insights%20from%20data%20collected%20in%201986.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Affelia%20Wibisono%20of%20the%20Dublin%20Institute%20of%20Advanced%20Studies%2C%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20research%2C%20described%20the%20findings%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20the%20importance%20of%20re-examining%20old%20data%2C%20as%20new%20discoveries%20may%20be%20hidden%20within%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20is%20already%20planning%20a%20return%20mission%20to%20Uranus%2C%20the%20Uranus%20Orbiter%20and%20Probe%2C%20expected%20to%20launch%20in%20the%20next%20decade.%20Dr.%20Jamie%20Jasinski%20from%20NASA%2C%20who%20led%20the%20re-ana