67.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fis-elon-musk-still-at-mar-a-lago-dining-and-playing-golf-with-donald-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F115221567.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUnless%20PCB%20Decides%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20ICC's%20New%20Plan%20On%20Champions%20Trophy%20Revealed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20has%20sought%20a%20response%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20on%20hosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%20following%20India's%20refusal%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20country%20for%20the%20tournament.%20The%20PCB%20on%20Sunday%20had%20confirmed%20that%20it%20received%20an%20email%20from%20the%20ICC%20that%20India%20declined%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20country.%20%26quot%3BUnless%20the%20PCB%20decides%20to%20pull%20out%20of%20hosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20the%20current%20plan%20is%20to%20hold%20India's%20matches%20in%20UAE%20and%20the%20final%20in%20Dubai%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20Cricket%20Board%20has%20told%20the%20ICC%20that%20a%20Hybrid%20Model%20is%20acceptable%20to%20them%20only%20if%20the%20final%20is%20held%20in%20Dubai%20and%20not%20in%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20on%20Monday%20remained%20silent%20without%20giving%20any%20reaction%20to%20the%20BCCI%20informing%20the%20ICC%20it%20will%20not%20send%20its%20team%20to%20play%20in%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20But%20according%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20ICC%20has%20asked%20the%20PCB%20to%20confirm%20if%20a%20Hybrid%20Model%20-%20where%20India's%20matches%20and%20the%20final%20would%20be%20held%20in%20Dubai%20-%20is%20acceptable%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20has%20assured%20the%20PCB%20that%2C%20under%20this%20arrangement%2C%20they%20would%20receive%20full%20hosting%20fees%20and%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20has%20told%20the%20PCB%20that%20if%20it%20decides%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20hosting%20of%20the%20mega%20event%20on%20a%20Hybrid%20Model%20it%20would%20get%20its%20full%20hosting%20fees%20and%20majority%20of%20the%20matches%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20the%20PCB%20decides%20to%20pull%20out%20of%20hosting%20the%20tournament%20due%20to%20India's%20refusal%2C%20the%20ICC%20could%20consider%20moving%20the%20entire%20event%20to%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20PCB%20source%20had%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20talk%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20Hybrid%20Model%20as%20of%20now%20and%20they%20would%20seek%20further%20clarity%20from%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20talk%20about%20having%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20on%20a%20Hybrid%20Model%20system%20as%20of%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reliable%20PCB%20source%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20email%20is%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20ICC%20with%20the%20advice%20of%20its%20legal%20department%20in%20which%20the%20Board%20wanted%20clarifications%20from%20the%20ICC%20on%20the%20Indian%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20of%20now%20the%20entire%20situation%20is%20being%20gauged%20by%20the%20PCB.%20No%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20on%20the%20next%20step.%20Yes%20the%20PCB%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20government%20for%20consultation%20and%20directives%20if%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Pakistani%20media%20speculated%20on%20potential%20responses%2C%20including%20the%20Pakistan%20government%20advising%20the%20PCB%20to%20avoid%20playing%20India%20altogether%20or%20the%20PCB%20pursuing%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20ICC%20and%20BCCI%20at%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20in%20Geneva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20not%20travelled%20