l%20benefits.%20Its%20immune-boosting%20properties%20make%20it%20a%20great%20addition%20to%20winter%20diets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FxvgitzkvXRQ%3Fsi%3Dv3Ene2sVGPnousEU%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshakarkandi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroasted%20with%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20drenched%20in%20lemon%20juice%20makes%20for%20a%20perfect%20binge%20feast.%20It%20necessitates%20no%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20sugar%2C%20or%20oil.%20The%20natural%20sweetness%20of%20roasted%20or%20boiled%20sweet%20potatoes%20pairs%20beautifully%20with%20the%20savoury%2C%20tangy%2C%20and%20spicy%20ingredients%20used%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Echaat%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20%3Cem%3ESarson%20Gosht%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20didn%E2%80%99t%20presume%20we%E2%80%99d%20frame%20a%20list%20of%20winter%20recipes%20and%20leave%20out%20a%20%3Cem%3Esarson%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mustard)%20rendition%2C%20did%20you%3F%20For%20eons%2C%20%3Cem%3Esarson%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316022%2Fcan-mustard-help-manage-covid-immunity-respiratory-infections-food-science%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecult%20favourite%20of%20winter%20menus%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%2C%20a%20characteristic%20of%20North%20Indian%20gastronomy%20in%20particular.%20With%20the%20smorgasbord%20of%20options%20that%20feature%20this%20timeless%20ingredient%2C%20it%20is%20a%20tough%20call%20to%20narrow%20down%20on%20any%20one%20recipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D476%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252FChefSan