s%20a%20blessed%20and%20beautiful%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akriti%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20scope%20for%20tourism%20there%3B%20lots%20of%20restaurants%20and%20campsites%20have%20come%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20problem%2C%20the%20West%20Kameng%20administration%20is%20actively%20working%20to%20spread%20awareness.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20it%20is%20the%20community%20that%20needs%20to%20take%20the%20lead%3B%20only%20the%20communities%20can%20educate%20the%20tourists%20not%20to%20litter%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akriti%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20community-driven%20areas%2C%20and%20here%20the%20feeling%20of%20community%20is%20quite%20high.%20Communities%20have%20been%20sensitised%20not%20to%20let%20tourists%20litter%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20we%20have%20designated%20places%20where%20plastic%20waste%20can%20be%20stored.%20We%20then%20collect%20it%20and%20dispose%20of%20it%20at%20the%20appropriate%20site%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPema%20Sangay%20%E2%80%94%20who%20runs%20a%20homestay%20in%20the%20village%20and%20has%20actively%20embraced%20the%20zero-waste%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20says%20that%20all%20his%20guests%20are%20educated%20about%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20zero-waste%20initiative%20and%20requested%20to%20keep%20their%20waste%20segregated%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202648px)%20100vw%2C%202648px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FDoor-to-door-campaign_11zon-1730809788.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spreading%20awareness%2C%20one%20doorstep%20at%20a%20time%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FDoor-to-door-campaign_11zon-1730809788.jpg%202648w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FDoor-to-door-campaign_11zon-